Task Set 2: Lambda with Parameters

Task 2.1 – Lambda with Single Parameter
Create a new functional interface called NameGreeter with:
void greet(String name);
In LambdaBasicDemo, implement this using a lambda that prints "Hi <name>".

Task 2.2 – Lambda with Multiple Parameters and Return
Create another functional interface called Adder:
int add(int a, int b);
Implement this using a lambda in the same main() method that returns the sum and print the result.

